<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-05-26T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-05-26T00:00:00-05:00" n="972" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d972">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">895.01/251</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">Major General <persName type="from">Edwin M.
                                        Watson</persName>, Secretary to President
                                        <persName>Roosevelt</persName>, to the Chairman of the
                                    Korean Commission in the United States</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Rhee</hi></persName>)</head>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, [<date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-05-26">May 26,
                                    1943</date>.]</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">My Dear Dr. Rhee</hi>: By direction of the
                                President, I acknowledge the receipt of your letter of May 15, 1943,
                                in which you discuss various matters relating to Korea and with
                                which you enclose a copy of a telegram from Mr. Tjosowang.</p>
                            <p>I do not need to assure you that the contents of your letter and its
                                enclosures have received careful attention.</p>
                            <p>Very sincerely yours,</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Edwin</hi> M. <hi rend="smallcaps">Watson</hi>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>